    },
    {
      "id": "fmXOMAbCug64v1aD_Lsor",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 172.71825398207977,
      "y": 1249.9133826760142,
      "width": 700.2692747651861,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffd8a8",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 70,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aW",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1310906270,
      "version": 560,
      "versionNonce": 969670158,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781954467768,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Now suppose, we want to add more functions to Document abstract\nclass and that is scanForVirus(), getMetaProperties().\n\nSo all concrete classes implementing it will also need to be updated.\nThis in turn breaks SOLID principles: OCP, SRP & also gets Complex",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Now suppose, we want to add more functions to Document abstract class and that is scanForVirus(), getMetaProperties().\n\nSo all concrete classes implementing it will also need to be updated.\nThis in turn breaks SOLID principles: OCP, SRP & also gets Complex",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "3t6LlipZsEXdMqvU9oJZ4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 769.109493625998,
      "y": 1505.4125013636456,
      "width": 91.01266479492188,
      "height": 17.693032070400807,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "RK82hindUkd9tVziBY1AD"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aX",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 456763650,
      "version": 930,
      "versionNonce": 1945963598,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781954467768,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "<<abstract>>",
      "fontSize": 14.154425656320646,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "<<abstract>>",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "9hUR8-CtgPWe4Ci_FwMgj",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 178.52588796798113,
      "y": 1406.1544482839079,
      "width": 691.6697357716023,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffd8a8",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 70,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aY",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 498073538,
      "version": 398,
      "versionNonce": 1500664462,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781954467768,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "As we remember basic ideology of Design-Pattern is to extract out\nwhatever changes often out of the classes.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "As we remember basic ideology of Design-Pattern is to extract out whatever changes often out of the classes.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "11k8zijICrobzW-R7f5Zz",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 147.62456505383145,
      "y": 1950.2843122845977,
      "width": 978.3792724609375,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffd8a8",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 70,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aZ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 820618462,
      "version": 382,
      "versionNonce": 1692717262,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781954467768,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Here, we're moving with assumption that, we won't be adding new Concrete classes often (less-likely)\nbut instead we will be mostly focusing on adding new functionalities (more-likely changes)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Here, we're moving with assumption that, we won't be adding new Concrete classes often (less-likely)\nbut instead we will be mostly focusing on adding new functionalities (more-likely changes)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
